      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's... an unusual way to put it. Let's try to stay focused on the technical side. \n\nRegarding the \"phantom stock\" or system glitches you mentioned, could you go into more detail about how a lag between the physical movement of the EC-1105 microchips and the WMS update might cause these specific, small-scale numbers? I'm trying to determine if this is a data synchronization issue or something else.",
      "source": "evaluator"
